{
  "3189320": {
    "name": "Ophelia",
    "steam_appid": 3189320,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189320/extras/df0052e47fc3c0243a898c2aa2f5b711.webp?t=1730809886\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You haven't heard a word from your sister since your quarrel. Nevertheless, you receive a letter asking you to visit her. Hesitantly, you accept her invitation to her island, where an uneasy feeling quickly spreads through you. There seems to be something wrong with the place and the people and there is no sign of Ophelia.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189320/extras/2b6257342d32622cd04507b451219ddb.webp?t=1730809886\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore Ophelia's house and the surrounding area for numerous secrets. But it's not just the present that's worth exploring and taking a closer look at, but also your past. Discover every hidden nook and cranny, examine all the boxes and open all the doors. What is hidden behind them can certainly help you on your quest. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189320/extras/1e4b83450f70d4eaaca921b077c83e9e.poster.avif?t=1730809886\" width=600 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189320/extras/1e4b83450f70d4eaaca921b077c83e9e.webm?t=1730809886\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189320/extras/56c3c98ddf64538ffd761a48e0129a7d.webp?t=1730809886\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Examine all the objects you have found thoroughly. Some will bring back old memories, others will contain clues or help you in some other way to complete your quest. So read carefully what your collection has to offer, because an insignificant detail may make your search easier. Some items reveal their full potential, but only when they are combined with other objects to create something new.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189320/extras/9a498d0fa01f0a77b0aad710b065f73d.poster.avif?t=1730809886\" width=600 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189320/extras/9a498d0fa01f0a77b0aad710b065f73d.webm?t=1730809886\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189320/extras/f331bd8187b9b8c7f3ac97ab8c199911.webp?t=1730809886\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve a variety of puzzles. The information you gain on your adventure will sometimes help you with these, so pay attention. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189320/extras/45ada831a909108d919d3cb3496123f3.poster.avif?t=1730809886\" width=600 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189320/extras/45ada831a909108d919d3cb3496123f3.webm?t=1730809886\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189320/extras/a43b0ca74f5062f528fe49b7538591e6.webp?t=1730809886\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stabilize and calm down from time to time. The mysterious surroundings can have a strong influence on your thoughts and concentration. Many things that otherwise seem obvious are perceived differently or not at all when you are stressed. So make sure that your mental resilience is not stretched too thin.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189320/extras/dae31b78555e9c5ec207dbd5e4613afa.poster.avif?t=1730809886\" width=600 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189320/extras/dae31b78555e9c5ec207dbd5e4613afa.webm?t=1730809886\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once the threat of the island has taken hold of you, you will find it very difficult to escape. It will engulf you in its darkness and possibly destroy your search for Ophelia.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189320/extras/f98a2377c5003a9df21b0b3f8a229f99.webp?t=1730809886\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p>",
